               "history": [
                  {
                     "text": "#### The haplogroup\n\nAlthough we have not found a specific mention of the haplogroup of the inhabitants of the Folsom region, we follow the conclusion of the study by Fagundes, N. J. R. *et al* to assign haplogroup B2 to this person (<htcite0>).\n\n#### Tools\n\nIn Folsom, various points were also found that, due to their shape, were probably produced in series, in a standardized manner, to be incorporated into local tools (<htcite1>).\n\nAn evolution of tools is also observed in the Folsom region, such as the appearance of possible stone knives and the use of *atlatls* (<htcite2>; <htcite3>). Esta evolución nos lleva a otra reflexión.",
