                     "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgAtlatl\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAtlatl', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 7</b>: Ornamental profile of a warrior. © The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York (<htcite0> ).</p>",
